    "description": "《青夏轨迹》是日本美少女游戏资深大厂GIGA/Entergram出品的一部青春题材的视觉小说。本作由在动画与轻小说界均有活跃的知名插画家U35负责原画与角色设计，由大地小猫与冬野胴服联袂担当剧本。由新锐音乐人虾丸咖喱伯爵制作音乐。人气声优小鸟居夕花、夏和小、和实羽优希为本作女主角献声。片头主题歌由超人气歌姬KOTOKO献唱，片尾主题歌由新锐歌姬紫咲萤献唱。<br><br>本作发售后赢得市场普遍赞誉，并荣获萌系游戏大赏年度剧本金奖等诸多奖项。  此后陆续在PlayStation4、PlayStation Vita和Nintendo Switch平台推出家用机版。Steam版本将拥有1920X1080的高清画质。预定将于2022年11月推出。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185800/extras/story.png?t=1666778391\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185800/extras/2210210242dNp2QalVOYLxzrVJkVzBbW3kXK51J0.jpg?t=1666778391\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185800/extras/2210210244XZAoqDgRrJO3y450j6zpG5xWLNe7wk.jpg?t=1666778391\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185800/extras/2210210246nYeZKbq2oV0kyWdRjOzB56xXONDa9m.jpg?t=1666778391\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185800/extras/22102102471Lb7olNPpKYxvPL0pnv083Gd6wZD5W.jpg?t=1666778391\" /></span>",
